FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /app

COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve

COPY . .
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

WORKDIR /app

RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ca-certificates && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

RUN mkdir -p /tmp/certs && \
    cd /tmp/certs && \
    curl -o rds-ca.pem https://truststore.pem.mzstatic.com/MzStoreServices.cer 2>/dev/null || echo "RDS cert download note: use your actual RDS CA URL" && \
    curl -o digicert.pem https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt 2>/dev/null || echo "DigiCert cert download note" && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca -file rds-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt 2>/dev/null || true && \
    keytool -import -alias digicert-azure -file digicert.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt 2>/dev/null || true && \
    cd / && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs

RUN addgroup -S appgroup && \
    adduser -S -u 1001 -G appgroup app

COPY --from=builder /app/target/app.jar /app/app.jar

RUN chown -R app:appgroup /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=10s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Java Analytics Dashboard"

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
